<title>Angelte Lai Lenna</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungngaih mel him him a um puoi,
 Angelte lailenna achun;
 Khawvel lungngaih thuoka tauten,
 Kahlai haiin Lalpa bel ui.

[V2]
 Lalpa zie gam chu ei thil sakin,
 Zie khawvela ka lenlai hin;
 Lungkham thuok a ka kahna hi,
 Aw nem takin hun thuok ingka.

[V3]
 2. Aw zie muna lengte haw chun,
 A khensa teu ngaih lohna di'n;
 Hinna lungmuon tui a dawn ui,
 Heiloh pakcha le a thiek ui.

[V4]
 3. En zel leuhing mun lopi chu,
 Angel vam leh Zingsawl Aksi;
 Khawvui a kai lung a hel diek,
 Belam No tuollenna gam chu.

[V5]
 4. Mun lopi chu ka tun tiengleh,
 Keile Lalpan ei umpih ding;
 Angel thieng zalaia buolin,
 Kumsawt in Lalpa chawian ka.</lyrics>
</song>